data.introduce: 该接口对应主机指令ESYC。用于获取IET协议相关信息。
data.business: 本接口业务范围与黑屏ESYC指令一致，可支持查询与某个航司有IET协议的航空公司列表，以及支持指定查询两家航空公司是否有IET协议。
data.functions:
本接口支持功能如下：
1、指定查询与某个航司有IET协议的航空公司
2、指定查询两家航空公司是否有IET协议
data.requestSchema: [{"name":"TES_AirESYCDataRQ","type":"object","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"提取预订信息请求","children":[{"name":"POS","type":"object","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"Point Of Sale","children":[{"name":"Source","type":"object","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"请求者信息","children":[{"name":"@PseudoCityCode","type":"string","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"伪城市代码（Office代码：PKE099）","children":[]}]}]},{"name":"AirlineCodeInfo","type":"object","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"","children":[{"name":"AirlineCode","type":"string","quantity":"1..2","default":"","description":"航空公司二字码，当HasESYC值位true时需要传两个此节点，为false值时需要传一个此节点","children":[]}]},{"name":"@HasESYC","type":"boolean","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"值为true时表示：指定查询两家航空公司是否有IET协议字段说明，此时AirlineCode节点有且仅有2个；为false值表示：指定查询与某个航司有IET协议的航空公司字段说明，此时AirlineCode节点有且仅有1个。","children":[]}]}]

odeInfo","type":"array","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"与请求中airlineID对应的航空公司有IET协议的航司两字代码数组","children":[{"name":"AirlineCode","type":"string","quantity":"1..n","default":"","description":"航空公司二字码","children":[]}]},{"name":"Remark","type":"string","quantity":"1","default":"","description":"主机返回第一行内容","children":[]}]}]}]
